dataset.title: Zoning
dataset.description: This is a polygon geodatabase depicting the local zoning of parcels under Outagamie County Zoning jurisdiction. Outagamie County created new zoning maps for the areas of the County that have exclusive agriculture zoning that are under County jurisdiction. The County also updated the text of the County Zoning Ordinance to meet requirements enforced by DATCP to meet requirements of chapter 91 of the Wisconsin State Statutes dealing with farmland preservation starting in 2013.

dataset.title: Airport Zoning

dataset.title: Cadastral FGDB Download
dataset.description: This dataset includes the following layers: Block Number Text, Lot Lines, CSM Text, Deed Acre Text, Display Lines, Government Lot Text, Lot Dimension Text, Lot Number Text, Municipality Boundaries, Parcel Polygons, Parcel Note Text, Plat Name Text, Plat Polygons, Private Claim Text, Right of Way Polygons, Right of Way Text, Parcel Number Text, Water Text. All Data is available in File Geodatabse format which will include all annotation.
